# 16. Build Flow

Compile

↓

Elaborate

↓

Run Test

↓

Generate Log

↓

Generate Coverage

↓

Regression Summary

---

# 17. Debug Methodology

Primary debug sources:

1. Simulation Log

2. Scoreboard Messages

3. Assertion Failures

4. Waveforms

---

Recommended waveform groups:

APB Signals

AXI Signals

Register Bank

Interrupts

DMA State Machine

---

# 18. Regression Strategy

Smoke Regression

```
Basic functionality
```

Block Regression

```
GPIO
TIMER
DMA
```

Protocol Regression

```
APB
AXI
```

Full Regression

```
Entire test suite
```

---

# 19. UVM Migration Readiness

The architecture is intentionally designed so that later migration to UVM is straightforward.

Mapping:

APB BFM
→ UVM Driver

Monitor
→ UVM Monitor

Transaction Class
→ Sequence Item

Scoreboard
→ UVM Scoreboard

Coverage
→ Subscriber/Coverage Collector

Tests
→ UVM Sequences

End of Document
